hisi-crypto-ws63

The WS63 security-accelerator register behavior and operation sequencing used
by this crate were derived from and checked against the HiSilicon WS63
`security_unified` driver sources distributed under the Apache License,
Version 2.0 in the fbb_ws63 source tree.

Copyright (c) HiSilicon (Shanghai) Technologies Co., Ltd. 2023-2023.

The Rust implementation has been substantially modified and independently
structured for `no_std` Rust. Changes include typed peripheral ownership,
fallible capability traits, bounded polling, PAC-generated register access,
explicit cache maintenance, secret clearing, and removal of the original OS,
allocator, and service-layer dependencies.
